name: Futa frontal 1 - Hypernetwork
description:
This hypernetwork turns all girls into dick girls. It was trained on Anything-V3.0, but can also be used with other anime style models with varying degrees of success.

Feb 11 2023: This hypernetwork has been upgraded to Futa frontal 2 (LoRA), which creates higher quality 2.5D images. I recommend you download that LoRA instead of this hypernetwork.

Use instructions:

For best results use with models that focus on anime and use Danbooru tags. Good models that I've found to use it with are: Anything-V3.0 / 4.5 (4.5 for 2.5D, 3.0 for 2D), AbyssOrangeMix2, SimpMaker 3k3, and a mix of Anything + HassanBlend.

It performs poorly with models that have a photorealistic focus, such as: f222, SXD, HassanBlend, URPM, SD1.5.

Recommended hypernetwork strength: 0.8

The training data was 512x640 resolution so expect the best results when using that resolution, but it still works just fine at 512x512.

For prompting you need to include Danbooru tags since the hypernetwork was trained with WD14/Danbooru captions. Unlike Anything-V3.0, leaving the prompt text box empty will give terrible results. At minimum you need to prompt for "1girl, futanari, penis", and the more specific you get with your prompt the better the results will be.

Embeddings that were created with photorealistic people also work well as long as they aren't overtrained.

You will need to use a VAE in order to not get desaturated images.

See below for more example prompts.

Training info:

The hypernetwork was trained on 186 high quality anime style images captioned with WD14/Danbooru tags at 512x640 resolution. In order to reduce the horror that is multiple penises growing out in multiple directions, the types of images were restricted to mostly frontal images. This helps make the penis generation more consistent, but reduces the flexibility in poses you can ask it to do. Very large penises/boobs were filtered out to give the generated images more realistic sized anatomy.

Install:

For Automatic1111, install like any other hypernetwork by putting the .pt file in the stable-diffusion-webui/models/hypernetworks folder. Make sure to enable the hypernetwork in the Settings tab, and set the hypernetwork strength to 0.8.

Example prompts:

Many of the preview images used these prompts. For exact generation details, click the white ( i ) button on the bottom right of each preview image. All images were made at 512x640 resolution and upscaled by 2x with hires fix turned on.
